title: Oscar D'vine - Just Do It (Single) New EDM 2014 Daft Punk
description:
320 Kbit/s
44.1 khz
Club Mix 
Radio Mix

Influenced and inspired by artists like Daft Punk, Wolfgang Gartner and other EDM artists, swedish wiz kid DJ/Producer Oscar D'vine has shaped his own very unique EDM style. Following up his first amazing track "Blow Off" which literally blew our minds when we first heard it, he now serves us a similar tune which just sticks on to your mind after playing it just once.
A hard driven beat, massive side chained keyboards and bass, alongside funky melodic vocoder voices makes it to a powerful EDM track. 
Available Mixes: Club Mix & Radio Mix
Mastering: Mutant Bit Mastering
